fr.ign.cogit.geoxygene.spatial.geomaggr

Class GM_Aggregate<GeomType extends IGeometry>

  • Object
    • GM_Object
      • GM_Aggregate<GeomType>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAggregate<GeomType>, IGeometry, Cloneable, Iterable<GeomType>, Collection<GeomType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GM_MultiCurve, GM_MultiPoint, GM_MultiSolid, GM_MultiSurface

    public class GM_Aggregate<GeomType extends IGeometry>
extends GM_Object
implements Collection<GeomType>, IAggregate<GeomType>
    Agrégation quelconque d'objets géométriques. Il n'y a aucune structure interne. On aurait pu faire un set d'elements au lieu d'une liste ?
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Thierry Badard & Arnaud Braun
